query:
SELECT t.id as tenant_id, t.name as company_name, u.email, u.name as user_name, ts.id as subscription_id
FROM tenants t
LEFT JOIN users u ON u.tenantId = t.id AND u.isSuperAdmin = 1
LEFT JOIN tenantSubscriptions ts ON ts.tenantId = t.id
WHERE ts.id IS NULL
ORDER BY t.id DESC;
